animeTitle: Kamen Rider SD Kaiki?! Kumo Otoko
animeDescription: This OVA is a parody of the popular japanese Tokusatsu (Power Ranger/Ultraman genre) franchise Kamen Rider. It features all of the Kamen Riders from The Original to Shin (Shin only makes a cameo). See More Info for a more detailed synopsis.
